{"tid":2076155,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"新冷戰隨時爆發，香港黃藍之分就係新嘅柏林圍牆","createTime":"2020-06-23T10:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T17:06:50.000Z","uid":40431,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"95326af45471102e8dacc9f13fafcc97d789d8ea","tid":2076155,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/secretary-michael-r-pompeo-at-the-virtual-copenhagen-democracy-summit/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fsecretary-michael-r-pompeo-at-the-virtual-copenhagen-democracy-summit%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JZ0arUk5yypfOu6hIjalRP8%3D&h=4f43b5b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/secretary-michael-r-pompeo-at-the-virtual-copenhagen-democracy-summit/</a><br />\n<br />\n6月19號Pompeo喺哥本哈根民主峰會已經講得好明白，佢呼籲歐洲各國「喺自由同暴政之間作出選擇」，亦指出中共企圖破壞自由社會，建立一套以中共為中心嘅世界新秩序。：<br />\n<br />\n &quot;I know that there&rsquo;s fear in Europe that the United States wants you to choose between us and China.<br />\n<br />\nBut that&rsquo;s simply not the case.  <span style=\"color: red;\">It&rsquo;s the Chinese Communist Party&rsquo;s that&rsquo;s forcing this choice.  The choice isn&rsquo;t between the United States; it&rsquo;s between freedom and tyranny.</span><br />\n<br />\nThe party wants you to throw away the progress we in the free world have made, through NATO and other institutions &ndash; both formal and informal institutions &ndash; and <span style=\"color: red;\">adopt a new set of rules and norms to accommodate them within Beijing.</span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n同時佢都清楚表明歐美應該聯手對抗極權：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">I don&rsquo;t believe that there&rsquo;s a uniquely &ldquo;European&rdquo; or &ldquo;American&rdquo; way to face this choice.  There&rsquo;s also no way to straddle these alternatives without abandoning who we are.  Democracies that are dependent on authoritarians are not worthy of their name.</span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅一句：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;But democracy isn&rsquo;t fragile in the way the Chinese Communist Party believes it is.  Democracy is strong.  We defeated fascism.  We won the Cold War.&quot;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n民主並唔係中共想像中咁脆弱，佢哋打敗過法西斯，贏過冷戰，換言之，今時今日，中共就係新一個崛起嘅極權，民主國家嘅敵對陣營。<br />\n<br />\n香港首當其衝，就係自由社會對抗中共嘅最前線，甚至係呢一場意識形態衝突嘅中心。黃藍嘅意識形態之爭就好似一道無形嘅柏林圍牆咁清楚分隔兩個陣營。我哋亦都注定要打呢一場意識形態戰，都好多人講過，眼前嘅選擇得返一個：<span style=\"color: red;\">對中共投降或者奮戰到底</span>。<br />\n<br />\n好多淺黃甚至深黃諗到對手係中共，可能會覺得無力，就好似今次國安法，香港人好似影響唔到結果，但係要知道我哋企喺民主自由嘅一方，極權最終都會被推倒。<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人「獨立」嘅意識經過幾年已經漸漸普遍、成熟，但係「反共」嘅意識先係打贏呢一場仗嘅關鍵。</span>"},{"pid":"d987e81782f98338f5838a21666faf3e35f4d957","tid":2076155,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:13:45.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6101966c122f8badedbc0b375f8ac257d119d4b1","tid":2076155,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40b18938ba547a8e63423ffb5d75da7640652cc","tid":2076155,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:52:40.000Z","msg":"最尾一句真係be water<br />\n唔好教條主義"},{"pid":"a943ae7b17c8b0debdd3ad0af2006f9ca92068ba","tid":2076155,"uid":254684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:53:29.000Z","msg":"係閪咩"},{"pid":"66f631a4a46092b8f257804a7f67eb674741edc0","tid":2076155,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.